<HEAD>With AM-Inaugural Rdp, Bjt</HEAD>
<HEAD>Tight Security, Protests Planned for Inauguration</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By CAROLYN SKORNECK</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>WASHINGTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
 The bullet-proof shield to protect <PERSON> George </PERSON> <PERSON> Bush </PERSON> when he takes the presidential oath of office Friday is in place. The manhole covers along the parade route are welded shut. Virtually every police agency in town has canceled all days off. Welcome to <LOCATION> Washington </LOCATION>, the inaugural city, where protestors are ready to demonstrate for their own version of a `` kinder, gentler'' nation and authorities hope they're ready for whatever transpires. `` We intend to be everywhere,'' <PERSON> Lisa </PERSON> <PERSON> Fithian </PERSON>, a spokeswoman for the Counter-Inaugural Coalition for a <ORGANIZATION> People </ORGANIZATION><ORGANIZATION> 's </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Agenda </ORGANIZATION>, told a news conference Wednesday. `` We will be a reminder of the urgency of not just a kinder, gentler nation but a kinder, gentler, less insulated government.'' But she said the coalition's 80 groups _ ranging from the <ORGANIZATION> Student </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Coalition </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Against </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Apartheid </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> and </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Racism </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> to </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Environmental </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Action </ORGANIZATION> _ have agreed not to conduct any civil disobedience. Anyone going anywhere the first families might go will be checked with metal detectors. That includes, for the first time, the 150,000 invited guests at the Capitol swearing-in ceremonies, even if they'll be sitting hundreds of yards away. That bit of security has upset Sen. <PERSON> Wendell </PERSON> <PERSON> Ford </PERSON>, D-Ky., chairman of the <ORGANIZATION> Joint </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Congressional </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Committee </ORGANIZATION> on Inaugural Ceremonies `` Security is something that bothers me considerably,'' he said Tuesday. `` We're a free and open nation insisting that those i